WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:04.720
To help Annika find Shiver, you need to listen for Shiver's giggling.

00:04.720 --> 00:08.560
The closer you are to her, the louder you'll hear her giggle.

00:08.560 --> 00:12.880
Use the arrow keys on the keyboard to move Annika around the room.

00:12.880 --> 00:17.600
When you think you've found Shiver's hiding spot, press the spacebar to take a look.

